PrecisSetting apart for the use and benefit of the POPLAR HILL BAND OF INDIANS of two parcels of land situate on the Berens River in the District of Kenora (Patricia Portion), in the Province of Ontario, which contain a total area of some 2.98 hectares, as an addition to Poplar Hill Indian Reserve.
